title: Beauty Report with Amy Morrison 10.05.2017 - 08 PM
description:
We're celebrating Amy's birthday tonight on the Beauty Report with lots of fun and surprises! Trish McEvoy, Matrix, Michael Todd and more are here with us. 
Amy shares her latest beauty tips and trends. From hair and makeup to skincare and fragrance, it's all new every week. Watch every Thursday 7 pm ET and 4 pm.
